      "writtenOn": "2019-10-21T19:38:38Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "detachPODAllocator (if renaming), or detachOpPODAllocator (if not), to be consistent with the member?  Or were we dropping \u0027allocator\u0027 to imply that the allocations into the arena were meant to be done?",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 56,
        "startChar": 34,
        "endLine": 56,
        "endChar": 45
